{"tid":1245824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰術帖】衝還衝，可唔可以顧下後面","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:13:47.000Z","uid":169366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d6990d77c21049f5e39098633345f19cfc7630","tid":1245824,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"呢期成日發夢，夢見成班朋友好鐘意向難關衝刺，但係次次衝完都話咁快比啲狗打番轉頭（尤其是喺煲底）。諗落因為大家都淨係記得向前衝，缺乏左啲兄弟喺旁邊做側翼、regroup同埋組防線閘，搞到每次啲狗過黎追果時，就只可以向後退，連搵中間關卡擋一擋都無。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJEY14O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJEY14O.png&h=3bb43fe1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果可以喺每一次都組到一個方陣各自分工，前兩排負責騎馬衝刺。後排留守負責叠馬組移動防線，會唔會較為理想？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbiCyb9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbiCyb9.png&h=1c50d4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6paTca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6paTca.png&h=d78b207f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣的話，就算衝到上前面比狗咬，都可以馬上回防有馬守住，不至於一打就散開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qih4dct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQih4dct.png&h=3854e2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰術討論，希望大家集思廣益，每日學習天天向上。"},{"pid":"3267c0b6721b41dee2e96e13754a341e0ee97452","tid":1245824,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2381b83796a84dab88ef9405edafb6577bd22bb","tid":1245824,"uid":108683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"反包圍的重要性"},{"pid":"47f79601890117487bbccb436d0b9a402d4d3198","tid":1245824,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2381b83796a84dab88ef9405edafb6577bd22bb","tid":1245824,"uid":108683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"反包圍的重要性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"不過講真，煲底真係易攻難守，狗仔出兵既路太多，個範圍又大勁難守。仲未計就算比你入到目標都仲有重馬騎唔郁，同埋厚玻璃。"},{"pid":"8a8589a88a97b46bce05a7cfb17b859844bb9314","tid":1245824,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"後面要緊貼，唔好得個睇字"},{"pid":"d2a9aa734ad12003c270daee3d61e57049612bbb","tid":1245824,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8589a88a97b46bce05a7cfb17b859844bb9314","tid":1245824,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"後面要緊貼，唔好得個睇字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"唔緊貼無所謂，幫手組下側翼做防手就好夠。<br />\n夠人夠馬起多兩重防線就可以擴大領地。<br />\n如果好彩有一邊箭頭衝得快啲仲可以反包圍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LV42Ksd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLV42Ksd.png&h=76fc6016&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔好淨係諗住推兵，而係要包圍玩消耗，撚狗咁撚<br />\n當佢地比人圍，一定會亂，到時就係我地贏"}]}